title: Bug 7752 - Export multiple files with same file name under different directories to zip file fails.
OB: When attempting to export multiple files with the same file name but from different directories to a zip file, the export process fails.
EB: The zip file should be able to successfully store files with the same name under different directories.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Create multiple files with the same name but in different directories. 
2. Attempt to export these files to a zip file using the export feature.
